On 2007-12-09 02:26:58 +0100, Vincent Lefevre wrote:
> prunille:~> incl="(-|)include"
> prunille:~> echo ${input##(-|)include ##}
> foo
> prunille:~> echo ${input##$incl ##}
> include foo

But:

prunille:~> echo ${input##${~incl} ##}
foo

The attached patch works, but I'm not sure it is correct.

